# ChatGPT Model Context Protocol (MCP) Configuration Reference

## 1. Web Integration (SSE Transport)
For ChatGPT Web via Chrome / Custom Connectors:
* **Transport Type**: SSE
* **URL**: https://flow.chatbulky.com/sse
* **Authentication**: None (Disable OAuth)

---

## 2. Desktop App Integration (Stdio Transport)
For ChatGPT Desktop / Claude Desktop configuration:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "flow": {
      "command": "docker",
      "args": [
        "exec",
        "-i",
        "flow-agent-server",
        "python3",
        "-u",
        "/app/flow_mcp_server.py"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```
